# Employee Attrition Dashboard – Power BI 📊

This is an interactive **Employee Attrition Analysis** dashboard built using **Power BI** to explore trends related to employee turnover, job satisfaction, salary hikes, and department-wise attrition risk.

---

## 🧠 Project Overview
The project identifies key patterns that contribute to employee attrition by analyzing various HR-related parameters. The goal is to uncover potential risk factors and guide HR teams to make data-driven decisions.

---

## 📁 Files Included
| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `Attrition project.pbix` | Power BI Dashboard file |
| `dataset.xlsx` | HR dataset used in the analysis |
| `Attrition project.pdf` | PDF version of dashboard/storyboard |
| `DashboardScreenshot.png` | Static snapshot of the dashboard |
| `Dashboard Record.gif` | Short dashboard interaction demo |

